✅ Read `.machine_readable/6a2/AGENTIC.a2ml` for interaction patterns
✅ Read `.claude/CLAUDE.md` for the language policy

## LIFECYCLE HOOKS

### on-enter (Session Start)

1. Read and acknowledge this manifest.
2. Read `.machine_readable/6a2/STATE.a2ml`; check for blockers and next actions.
3. State understanding of the canonical location.

### on-exit (Session End)

1. Update `.machine_readable/6a2/STATE.a2ml` if changes were made.
2. Document any new blockers and summarize outcomes.
3. Sync to the language tracker if available: `~/sync-language-tracker.sh`.

